<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 100px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .reservation-details {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .whatsapp-link {
            color: #25D366;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://bangteg.github.io/images/dampit-trans-logo.png" alt="Dampit Trans Logo" class="logo">
            <h2>New Reservation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello Admin,</p>
            <p>A new reservation has been made by <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>. Here are the details:</p>
            <div class="reservation-details">
                <p><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservation.id %></p>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %></p>
                <p><strong>Vehicle:</strong> <%= vehicle.name %></p>
                <p><strong>Units of Vehicles:</strong> <%= reservation.units %> unit(s)</p>
                <p><strong>Pick-up Location:</strong> <%= reservation.pickUp %></p>
                <p><strong>Drop-off Location:</strong> <%= reservation.dropOff %></p>
                <p><strong>Pick-up Date:</strong> <%= reservation.pickDate %></p>
                <p><strong>Drop-off Date:</strong> <%= reservation.dropDate %></p>
                <p><strong>Customer Contact:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/<%= user.contact %>" class="whatsapp-link"><%= user.contact %></a></p>
            </div>
            <p>Please validate the customer's data and contact them via WhatsApp before changing the reservation status.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you,</p>
            <p>Dampit Trans - Automated Messaging System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
